<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Evolution Tuition Centre | Build Your Child's Future</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #1a4a9e;
            --secondary-blue: #143a7a;
            --accent-yellow: #fbc02d;
            --text-white: #ffffff;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 74, 158, 0.9), rgba(20, 58, 122, 0.9)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497633762265-9d179a990aa6?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: var(--text-white);
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: var(--accent-yellow);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .welcome-badge {
            background-color: #d32f2f;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .tagline {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Content Section */
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: -40px auto 40px;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .feature-item i {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        /* Call to Action */
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .btn-call {
            background-color: var(--accent-yellow);
            color: #000;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .whatsapp-float {
            background-color: #25d366;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-call:hover, .whatsapp-float:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .limited-seats {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .container { margin: -20px 15px 40px; padding: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo-icon"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
        <p>✨ Unlock Your Child's True Potential! ✨</p>
        <h1>The Evolution Tuition Centre</h1>
        <div class="welcome-badge">Welcome to The Evolution</div>
        <p class="tagline">"With experienced educators and a student-first approach, we don't just teach... we build futures."</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                <div>Coaching for 1st to 12th Class</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i>
                <div>All Subjects (PSEB, CBSE, ICSE)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
                <div>Expert Guidance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <div>Focus on Concept Clarity & Results</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <a href="tel:9530750686" class="btn-call">
                <i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Call Now: 95307-50686
            </a>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/919530750686?text=I'm%20interested%20in%20enrolling%20my%20child%20at%20The%20Evolution%20Tuition%20Centre" class="whatsapp-float" target="_blank">
                <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp Us Today
            </a>

            <span class="limited-seats">
                <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i> Limited seats available — give your child the advantage they deserve!
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 The Evolution Tuition Centre. All Rights Reserved.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
